tasks.description:
Settings screen has several broken or placeholder features that must be fixed for production.

File: mobile/app/(protected)/settings.tsx (MODIFY)

1. FIX Restore Purchases (line 125-128):
- Currently just shows an Alert with static text, doesn't actually restore.
- Import `useSubscription` from '../../contexts/SubscriptionContext'.
- Get `handleRestore` from useSubscription().
- Replace the handleRestorePurchases function body with:
  ```
  hapticMedium();
  const restored = await handleRestore();
  if (restored) {
    hapticSuccess();
    Alert.alert('Success', 'Your purchases have been restored!');
  } else {
    Alert.alert('No Purchases Found', 'We could not find any previous purchases.');
  }
  ```

2. FIX Share App (line 111-118):
- Currently uses Linking.openURL to a placeholder Apple URL that doesn't exist yet.
- Import { Share } from 'react-native'.
- Replace handleShareApp with:
  ```
  hapticSelection();
  await Share.share({
    message: '✨ Check out AuraSnap — discover your aura energy with AI! Download now: https://apps.apple.com/app/aurasnap',
  });
  ```
- This uses the native share sheet (works even before App Store listing).

3. FIX Biometric Toggle Persistence:
- Import AsyncStorage from '@react-native-async-storage/async-storage'.
- On mount (in useEffect), load: `const saved = await AsyncStorage.getItem('biometric_enabled'); if (saved === 'true') setBiometricEnabled(true);`
- In the Switch onValueChange, save: `await AsyncStorage.setItem('biometric_enabled', String(newValue)); setBiometricEnabled(newValue);`
- Add hapticSelection() on toggle.

4. ADD Privacy Policy link:
- After the "Rate Us" row, add a "Privacy Policy" row with Ionicons name="shield-outline" size={20} color="#6b7280" in bg-gray-600/20 circle. On press: `Linking.openURL('https://aurasnap.app/privacy')`. This satisfies Apple Guideline 5.1.

5. ADD "Go Premium" button for non-subscribers:
- Import useSubscription, get isSubscribed.
- If !isSubscribed, show a prominent card above the App section: bg-gradient using nested Views with bg-violet-900/50 rounded-2xl p-5. Content: sparkles icon, "Unlock Premium" title in text-lg font-bold text-white, "Unlimited scans, no ads, full history" in text-sm text-gray-300, and a "Upgrade" button (bg-violet-600 rounded-full py-3 mt-3). On press: router.push('/paywall').
